snippet.title: Toki no Senshi - Chrono Soldier MAME Gameplay video Snapshot -Rom name tokisens-
snippet.description:
This video is a snapshot Toki no Senshi - Chrono Soldier game sample video. Currently I have over 4000 videos gameplays completing almost full MAME romset.

You can download this sample video to add in the frontend for GameEx, HyperSpin, Mala, MameWAH, Maximus Arcade, XBMC and more. Toki no Senshi - Chrono Soldier is a gameplay video demo rendered in high quality with a 480p resolution.

The original MAME rom name for this game is tokisens.
